    {
      "id": "8f1af753-942c-4d4b-aa38-0bc89ddee82f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Online learning has become increasingly popular even though it lacks formal communication channels for feedback. Authorsd propose a multi-dimensional time-series model that is able to consider multiple features of students: behavior, characteristics and even prior performance.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "8f1af753-942c-4d4b-aa38-0bc89ddee82f",
        "parent": {
