    {
      "id": "13bebae6-c845-4418-963e-b98dcd9a65a8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Results show that the model achieved close to 100% accuracy (?) on OULAD in the task of early detection of students at risk. Moreover, the model achieves 74% and 74% F1 score in the multiclass problem of OULAD. As usual in these papers, model beats all other models it is being benchmarked against.",
